<node CREATED="1566553055184" ID="ID_1127724242" MODIFIED="1566553055184" TEXT="I just asked an SQL related question and the first answer was: This is a situation where dynamic SQL is the way to go.As I had never heard of dynamic SQL before I immediately searched this site and the web for what it was. Wikipedia has no article with this title. The first Google results all point to user forums where people ask more or less related questions." />
