<node CREATED="1566553055184" ID="ID_1757849612" MODIFIED="1566553055184" TEXT="The concept of Dynamic SQL is one that allows you to build a SQL statement or a full batch of SQL code and present it as a character string. Then you can take this string and execute it. SQL Server gives us a couple of options to execute character strings as T-SQL Code." />
</node>
