<node CREATED="1566553055184" ID="ID_1091385678" MODIFIED="1566553055184" TEXT="Dynamic SQL is also used to generate PLSQL blocks at run-time. This process to generate Dynamic SQL through PLSQL code at run-time is called Dynamic SQL Processing Technique. Advantages of Dynamic SQL. When a developer is unaware of SQL parts such as table name column name number of parameters etc. Dynamic SQL is used." />
