<node CREATED="1566553055184" ID="ID_186539043" MODIFIED="1566553055184" TEXT="DBMS_SQL for Dynamic SQL. PL/SQL provide the DBMS_SQL package that allows you to work with dynamic SQL. The process of creating and executing the dynamic SQL contains the following process. OPEN CURSOR: The dynamic SQL will execute in the same way as a cursor. So in order to execute the SQL statement we must open the cursor." />
