<node CREATED="1566553055184" ID="ID_543116711" MODIFIED="1566553055184" TEXT="Dynamic Structured Query Language (SQL) is a SQL version that facilitates the generation of dynamic (or variable) program queries. Dynamic SQL allows a programmer to write code that automatically adjusts to varying databases environments servers or variables. Dynamic SQL statements are not embedded in the source program but stored as strings " />
