<node CREATED="1566553055194" ID="ID_1492092075" MODIFIED="1566553055194" TEXT="So what is the definition of 2nd normal form? 2NF &#226;&#8364;&#8220; Second Normal Form Definition. A table is in 2 nd Normal Form if: The table is in 1 st normal form and; All the non-key columns are dependent on the table&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s primary key. We already know about the 1 st normal form but what about the second requirement? Let me try to explain." />
