<node CREATED="1566553055195" ID="ID_522748931" MODIFIED="1566553055195" TEXT="Second Normal Form expects a table to be in first normal form and not have partial dependency in case of composite primary key for a table. In this tutorial we will learn what partial dependency is and how to remove it for second Normal form." />
