<node CREATED="1566553055195" ID="ID_1136693864" MODIFIED="1566553055195" TEXT="Second Normal Form (2NF) The next step is to transform the data in first normal form (1NF) into second normal form (2NF). The rule is: remove any non-key attributes that only depend on part of the table key to a new table.Ignore tables with (a) a simple key or (b) with no non-key attributes (these go straight to 2NF with no conversion)." />
