<node CREATED="1566553055195" ID="ID_546214841" MODIFIED="1566553055195" TEXT="A table is in a third normal form when the following conditions are met &#226;&#710;&#8217; It is in second normal form. All nonprimary fields are dependent on the primary key. The dependency of these non-primary fields is between the data. For example in the following table &#226;&#8364;&#8220; the street name city and the state are unbreakably bound to their zip code." />
