<node CREATED="1566553055195" ID="ID_1416081668" MODIFIED="1566553055195" TEXT="Boyce and Codd Normal Form (BCNF) Boyce and Codd Normal Form is a higher version of the Third Normal form. This form deals with certain type of anomaly that is not handled by 3NF. A 3NF table which does not have multiple overlapping candidate keys is said to be in BCNF." />
