<node CREATED="1566553055195" ID="ID_257978958" MODIFIED="1566553055195" TEXT="3NF Rules; Boyce-Codd Normal Form (BCNF) The inventor of the relational model Edgar Codd proposed the theory of normalization with the introduction of First Normal Form and he continued to extend theory with Second and Third Normal Form. Later he joined with Raymond F. Boyce to develop the theory of Boyce-Codd Normal Form." />
