<node CREATED="1566553055195" ID="ID_118742730" MODIFIED="1566553055195" TEXT="Third normal form (3NF) is the third step in normalizing a database and it builds on the first and second normal forms 1NF and 2NF. 3NF states that all column reference in referenced data that are not dependent on the primary key should be removed." />
