<node CREATED="1566553055196" ID="ID_219634009" MODIFIED="1566553055196" TEXT="Boyce&#226;&#8364;&#8220;Codd Normal Form (BCNF) - BCNF is an extension to Third Normal Form 3NF and is slightly stronger than 3NF A relation R is in BCNF if P Q is a trivial functional dependency and P is a superkey for R If a relation is in BCNF that would mean that redundancy based on fu" />
